transformations.description: This source is a custom query using a union. The first portion of the query will use the basicpolicy_stg, claimstats_stg, policystats_stg, risk_stg,  and line_stg tables. The second portion of the query will use the basicpolicyapp_stg, risk_application_stg, and line_stg tables.
transformations.name: src_query

object.customQuery:
select
distinct prkr.policy_system_id,
prkr.policy_cmm_container,
prkr.policy_reference_id,
prkr.shell_policy_indicator,
prkr.policy_company,
prkr.policy_number,
prkr.policy_module_number,
prkr.policy_key,
bp.controllingstatecd,
bp.subtypecd,
bp.tier,
b.tier as building_tier,
b.h107ind,
bp.effectivedt,
bp.expirationdt,
bp.inceptiondt,
th.transactiondt,
ad.agencycd,
ad.commercialname,
q.applicationnumber,
q.adduser,
q.adddt,
q.submitteddt,
tl.application_created_by_user,
tl.application_submitted_by_user,
tl.application_submitted_date,			
tgt.uw_dashboard_application_details_row_id, -- needed for expression in mapping
tgt.uw_dashboard_application_details_md5_hash_value -- needed for expression in mapping
from
dbo.basicpolicy_stg bp
left join dbo.policy_risk_key_reference prkr on
bp.systemid = prkr.policy_system_id
and bp.cmmcontainer = prkr.policy_cmm_container
left join 
(SELECT 
systemid, 
cmmcontainer, 
tier, 
h107ind,
rank() OVER (PARTITION BY systemid, cmmcontainer ORDER BY tier NULLS LAST, h107ind NULLS LAST ) AS rnk --added this per Dustin's recommendation
from
dbo.building_stg
WHERE status = 'Active') b on
bp.systemid = b.systemid
and bp.cmmcontainer = b.cmmcontainer
and bp.controllingstatecd in ('CT','NH','ME') --added this per Dustin's recommendation
AND b.rnk = 1
left join dbo.transactionhistory_stg th on
bp.systemid = th.systemid
and bp.cmmcontainer = th.cmmcontainer
and bp.id = th.parentid
and th.transactioncd = 'New Business'
left join dbo.quoteinfo_stg q on
bp.systemid = q.policyref
and q.applicationnumber <> ''
and q.status <>'Deleted' -- added per Shannon's commeent
left join (
select
distinct tl.idref,
tl.modelname,
max(case
when name = 'Application Assignment' then addedbyuserid
end) as application_created_by_user,
max(case
when name = 'Submit For Approval' then addedbyuserid
end) as application_submitted_by_user,
max(case
when name = 'Submit For Approval' then adddt
end) as application_submitted_date
from
dbo.task_stg t
join dbo.tasklink_stg tl 	  
on
tl.systemid = t.systemid
and tl.parentid = t.id
where "name" in ('Application Assignment', 'Submit For Approval')
group by
tl.idref,
tl.modelname ) tl on
bp.systemid = tl.idref
and bp.cmmcontainer = tl.modelname
left join dbo.agents_detail_stg ad on
bp.providerref = ad.systemid				
left join dbo.uw_dashboard_application_details tgt
on tgt.policy_system_id = bp.systemid 
and tgt.policy_cmm_container  = bp.cmmcontainer 
and coalesce(tgt.quote_application_number, '0') = coalesce(q.applicationnumber, '0')
and tgt.uw_dashboard_application_details_row_effective_end_date = '9999-12-31'
where
prkr.policy_risk_key_reference_row_effective_end_date = '9999-12-31'
AND prkr.policy_cmm_container = 'Policy'

union

select
distinct prkr.policy_system_id,
prkr.policy_cmm_container,
prkr.policy_reference_id,
prkr.shell_policy_indicator,
prkr.policy_company,
prkr.policy_number,
prkr.policy_module_number,
prkr.policy_key,
bpa.controllingstatecd,
bpa.subtypecd,
bpa.tier,
ba.building_application_tier as building_tier,
ba.building_application_h107_indicator,
bpa.effectivedt,
bpa.expirationdt,
bpa.inceptiondt,
th.transactiondt,
ad.agencycd,
ad.commercialname,
q.applicationnumber,
q.adduser,
q.adddt,
q.submitteddt,
tl.application_created_by_user,
tl.application_submitted_by_user,
tl.application_submitted_date,
tgt.uw_dashboard_application_details_row_id,
tgt.uw_dashboard_application_details_md5_hash_value
from
dbo.basicpolicyapp_stg bpa
left join dbo.policy_risk_key_reference prkr on
bpa.systemid = prkr.policy_system_id
and bpa.cmmcontainer = prkr.policy_cmm_container
left join 
(SELECT 
building_application_system_id, 
building_application_cmm_container, 
building_application_tier, 
building_application_h107_indicator,
rank() OVER (PARTITION BY building_application_system_id, building_application_cmm_container ORDER BY building_application_tier NULLS LAST, building_application_h107_indicator NULLS LAST ) AS rnk --added this per Dustin's recommendation
from
dbo.building_application_stg)ba
ON  
bpa.systemid = ba.building_application_system_id
and bpa.cmmcontainer = ba.building_application_cmm_container
and bpa.controllingstatecd in ('CT','NH','ME') --added this per Dustin's recommendation
AND ba.rnk = 1
left join dbo.transactionhistory_stg th on
bpa.systemid = th.systemid
and bpa.cmmcontainer = th.cmmcontainer
and bpa.id = th.parentid
and th.transactioncd = 'New Business'
left join dbo.quoteinfo_stg q on
bpa.systemid = q.systemid
and q.applicationnumber <> ''
and q.status <>'Deleted' -- added per Shannon's commeent
left join (
select
distinct tl.idref,
tl.modelname,
max(case
when name = 'Application Assignment' then addedbyuserid
end) as application_created_by_user,
max(case
when name = 'Submit For Approval' then addedbyuserid
end) as application_submitted_by_user,
max(case
when name = 'Submit For Approval' then adddt
end) as application_submitted_date
from
dbo.task_stg t
join dbo.tasklink_stg tl 
on
tl.systemid = t.systemid
and tl.parentid = t.id
where "name" in ('Application Assignment', 'Submit For Approval')
group by
tl.idref,
tl.modelname ) tl on
bpa.systemid = tl.idref
and bpa.cmmcontainer = tl.modelname
left join dbo.agents_detail_stg ad on
bpa.providerref = ad.systemid
left join dbo.uw_dashboard_application_details tgt
on tgt.policy_system_id = bpa.systemid 
and tgt.policy_cmm_container  = bpa.cmmcontainer 
and coalesce(tgt.quote_application_number, '0') = coalesce(q.applicationnumber, '0')
and tgt.uw_dashboard_application_details_row_effective_end_date = '9999-12-31'
where
prkr.policy_risk_key_reference_row_effective_end_date = '9999-12-31'
AND prkr.policy_cmm_container = 'Application'

transformations.description: This expression will implement logic for the following fields - policy_effective_date and policy_program_code. We will also create the hash key value for comparing data to the target.
transformations.name: exp_set_policy_details

fields.name: v_CT_ProgramCd
fields.expression:
DECODE(TRUE,
upper(h107ind) = 'YES', 'Select',
subtypecd = 'HO5' and in(tier, '-1', '1', '2', '3', '4', '5', '6', '7', '8'), 'Superior',
in(subtypecd, 'HO5T4', 'HO3') and in(tier, '-1', '1', '2', '3', '4', '5', '6', '7', '8'), 'Standard',
in(subtypecd, 'HO4', 'HO6') and in(tier, '1', '2', '3', '4', '5', '6', '7', '8'), 'Standard')

fields.name: v_NH_ProgramCd
fields.expression:
DECODE(TRUE,
upper(h107ind) = 'YES', 'Select',
subtypecd = 'HO5' and in(tier, '-1', '1', '2', '3', '4', '5', '6', '7', '8'), 'Superior',
in(subtypecd, 'HO5T4', 'HO3') and in(tier, '-1', '1', '2', '3', '4', '5', '6', '7', '8'), 'Standard',
in(subtypecd, 'HO4', 'HO6') and in(tier, '1', '2', '3', '4', '5', '6', '7', '8'), 'Standard')

fields.name: v_ME_ProgramCd
fields.expression:
DECODE(TRUE,
upper(h107ind) = 'YES', 'Select',
subtypecd = 'HO5' and in(tier, '1', '2', '3'), 'Superior',
subtypecd = 'HO5' and tier = '4', 'Standard',
in(subtypecd, 'HO3', 'HO5T4'), 'Standard',
in(subtypecd, 'HO4', 'HO6'), 'N/A')

fields.name: policy_program_code
fields.expression:
DECODE(TRUE,
controllingstatecd = 'CT' and in(policy_company,'Cambridge','Merrimack'), v_CT_ProgramCd,
controllingstatecd = 'NH' and in(policy_company,'Cambridge','Merrimack'), v_NH_ProgramCd,
controllingstatecd = 'ME' and in(policy_company,'Cambridge','Merrimack'), v_ME_ProgramCd)

fields.name: md5_hash_value
fields.expression:
MD5('policy_system_id' || to_char(policy_system_id) 
|| 'policy_cmm_container' || policy_cmm_container 
|| 'policy_reference_id' || policy_reference_id 
|| 'shell_policy_indicator' || shell_policy_indicator
|| 'policy_company' || policy_company
|| 'policy_number' || policy_number 
|| 'policy_module_number' || policy_module_number 
|| 'policy_key' || policy_key 
|| 'controllingstatecd' || controllingstatecd 
|| 'subtypecd' || subtypecd 
|| 'tier' || tier
|| 'building_tier' || to_char(building_tier)
|| 'h107ind' || h107ind
|| 'effectivedt' || to_char(effectivedt)
|| 'expirationdt' || to_char(expirationdt)
|| 'inceptiondt' || to_char(inceptiondt)
|| 'transactiondt' || to_char(transactiondt)
|| 'agencycd' || agencycd 
|| 'commercialname' || commercialname 
|| 'applicationnumber' || applicationnumber 
|| 'adduser' || adduser 
|| 'adddt' || to_char(adddt)
|| 'submitteddt' || to_char(submitteddt)
|| 'application_created_by_user' || application_created_by_user 
|| 'application_submitted_by_user' || application_submitted_by_user 
|| 'application_submitted_date' || to_char(application_submitted_date) )
